column2:
"You're here. I was waiting for you, <%me>.
I have something I wanted to ask you."
"I'd like to try fighting in a party of 4. Could you take me out with you again?"
"Asuna and I make two, then there's you, so we just need one more..."
"Of course, Matoi! It's about time all four of us got together, huh?"
"...That's OK, right? I hate having to keep leaning on you like this. I'll make up for it next time, count on it."
